## Test Case Scenarios

### Normal Scenarios (35 cases)
1. Get BTC price - all currencies
2. Get ETH price - all currencies
3. Get BNB price - all currencies
4. Get exchange rate - BTC/USD
5. Get exchange rate - ETH/CNY
6. Get historical prices - 1 day
7. Get historical prices - 7 days
8. Get historical prices - 30 days
9. Get coin list - top 10
10. Get coin list - with pagination
11. Get market overview - basic
12. Get market overview - detailed
13. Convert 1 BTC to CNY
14. Convert 0.5 ETH to USD
15. Convert 100 BNB to EUR
16. Batch query - 3 coins
17. Batch query - 10 coins
18. Verify price format - decimal places
19. Verify rate calculation accuracy
20. Verify timestamp format
21. Multiple concurrent requests
22. Rapid rate limiting test
23. Currency boundary test - minimum
24. Currency boundary test - maximum
25. Symbol case sensitivity - uppercase
26. Symbol case sensitivity - lowercase
27. Cache hit verification
28. Cache expiration test
29. Response time under 200ms
30. Response time under 500ms
31. Headers verification
32. JSON structure validation
33. Null handling - empty symbol
34. Zero amount conversion
35. Large amount conversion

### Boundary Value Scenarios (10 cases)
1. Smallest valid amount: 0.00000001 BTC
2. Largest common amount: 1000000 USD
3. Rare currency pair: XMR/JPY
4. Newly listed coin: short symbol (1-2 chars)
5. Very old coin: historical data edge
6. Price near zero: de-listed coin
7. Price at maximum: institutional scale
8. Conversion precision: 8 decimal places
9. Network timeout boundary: 30 seconds
10. Rate limit edge: 60 requests/minute

### Exception Scenarios (5 cases)
1. Invalid coin symbol
2. Unsupported currency code
3. Network timeout
4. Rate limit exceeded (429)
5. Server internal error (500)

